data.name: plFriendlyName.Help
data.value: Displays the name of the module.

data.name: plTitle.Help
data.value: Enter a title for the Module. This will appear in the Title Bar of the Container for this Module, if supported by the Container.

data.name: plAllTabs.Help
data.value: Select whether the module should appear in the same location on all pages of the site

data.name: plVisibility.Help
data.value: Choose the default visibility for this Module ie whether the module is collapsed or expanded.

data.name: plTab.Help
data.value: Move this module instance to another Page.

data.name: plHeader.Help
data.value: Enter header text for this Module

data.name: plFooter.Help
data.value: Enter footer text for this Module

data.name: plIcon.Help
data.value: Select an Icon for this Module to display in the Title Bar

data.name: plAlign.Help
data.value: Select the Alignment of the Module

data.name: plColor.Help
data.value: Enter a Color for the module

data.name: plBorder.Help
data.value: Enter a Border width for the Module

data.name: plModuleContainer.Help
data.value: Select a Container for the Module ( to add a new Container go to the File Manager)

data.name: plPermissions.Help
data.value: Select the View and Edit permissions by checking/unchecking the boxes in the grid. The module can inherit its permissions from the Page. To do this check the Inherit View Permissions checkbox.

data.name: plCacheTime.Help
data.value: Enter the time this object is kept in the Cache

data.name: plStartDate.Help
data.value: The start date for displaying this module. Prior to this date the module will only be visible to users with Manage permissions.

data.name: plEndDate.Help
data.value: The end date for displaying this module. After this date the module will only be visible to users with Manage permissions.

data.name: plDefault.Help
data.value: Select this option if you would like the Page Settings for this module to be used as the default settings when adding new modules. Option only available to Website Admins and SuperUsers.

data.name: plAllModules.Help
data.value: Select this option if you would like the Page Settings for this module to be applied to all existing modules in the site. Option only available to Website Admins and SuperUsers.

data.name: plDisplayTitle.Help
data.value: Select this option if you would like to display the Module container.

data.name: plDisplayPrint.Help
data.value: Select this option if you would like to enable printing on this module

data.name: plDisplaySyndicate.Help
data.value: Select this option if you would like to enable RSS on this module

data.name: ModuleHelp.Text
data.value:
Module Settings

Administrators can manage the Module Settings for the current Page. This allows you to specify characteristics of the module including content, permissions, and display properties.

data.name: valBorder.ErrorMessage
data.value: Invalid Border (must be a number between 0 and 9)

data.name: valEndDate2.ErrorMessage
data.value: End Date must be after Start Date

data.name: plNewTabs.Help
data.value: Check this box to add the module to new pages only. Option only available to Website Admins and SuperUsers.

data.name: plWebSlice.Help
data.value: Check this box to make this module an IE8 WebSlice

data.name: plWebSliceExpiry.Help
data.value: Enter a date when the Web Slice will expire - if left blank the Module's End date will be used

data.name: plWebSliceTitle.Help
data.value: Enter a title for the Web Slice - if you leave this blank the Module's Title will be used.

data.name: plWebSliceTTL.Help
data.value: Enter the Time to Live (TTL) for this web slice in minutes. If left blank this will default to the cache time (converted to minutes)

data.name: valWebSliceTTL.ErrorMessage
data.value: Invalid TTL - value must be an integer

data.name: InstalledOn.Text
data.value: This module has been added to the following pages:

data.name: InstalledOn.Help
data.value: Lists the pages that contain this module. An existing module can be added to other pages by using the Add Existing Module feature. This list only includes pages this module was added to using the Add Existing Module feature.

data.name: MsgInstalledOnNone.Text
data.value: This module instance has not been added to any additional pages.

data.name: MsgInstalledOnAll.Text
data.value: This module instance is displayed on all pages.

data.name: ModuleExists.Text
data.value: This module already exists on the target page (it may be in the recycle bin), and only one instance of a module can exist on a page.

data.name: CacheProvider.Help
data.value: Select the provider to use for this page.

data.name: CacheDuration.Help
data.value: Enter the duration (in seconds) to cache the page for. This must be an integer.

data.name: cmdClearTabModuleCache.Text
data.value: Clear Cache for This Tab Module

data.name: cmdClearAllTabModuleCache.Text
data.value: Clear Cache for All Tab Modules

data.name: lblCachedItemCount.Text
data.value: Current Cache Count: {0} item for this tab module

data.name: CacheDurationWarning.Text
data.value: This module has indicated a recommendation to disable caching (select NONE from the Output Cache Provider list above). Enabling caching on this module is not recommended and may cause the module to display stale data.

data.name: plTags.Help
data.value: Select items from the drop-down to tag this Module.

data.name: plAdminBorder.Help
data.value: Checking this box will enable red admin border to be displayed around the module to admins when logged on to the site.

data.name: defaultCultureLabel.Help
data.value: Click this link to view the version of this module in the default culture

data.name: PreviewNoSelectionMessage.Text
data.value: Please select a container to preview.

data.name: lblNoRecords.Text
data.value: This module has not been added to any other pages.

data.name: AllowIndexLabel.Help
data.value: This setting controls whether a module should be indexed by search crawlers.

data.name: isShareableLabel.Help
data.value: Check this box to allow the module to be shared across sites.

data.name: isShareableViewOnlyLabel.Help
data.value: Check this box to restrict the module to be shared as View Only.
